Hey guys, just wanted to share an exciting moment with you❤ So... today as I was prepping for our weekly Monday Meetings, I got an email from @forbes MAGAZINE letting me know that I've been listed as one of the top '10 FITNESS INFLUENCERS in the WORLD' on the Forbes List🌎 😱🤗... omg... truly honoured and taken aback... 🤗🙏🏽 ... Just wanted to say a little thank you to my most amazing team, my hubs/biz partner, The Hourglass & TWL squad and all of you for sharing in this fitness journey together because no accomplishment is ever done by just one person 👫👭👭Also congrats to everyone on this list, I'm honoured to be mentioned with such inspirational people. 
Also... just wanted to say... for anyone starting out and feel like the cards are stacked against you... I grew up in a single parent home, on welfare... I am naturally heavy and had anorexia through my teens/early 20's before I allowed myself to just be thick and learn to love it... magazines & products didn't want to work with me because I was not traditionally skinny or was to curvy to appeal to women... Any if these things could have stopped me because it wasn't easy and I had many, many doors slammed in my face... what kept me going was a strong belief in the value of the message that I was sharing, a strong work ethic and good positive people around me (like my hubs) not sugar coating anything, but pushing me and keeping me positive... what I'm saying here is we all have barriers, but we can't let them own us, or allow us to use them as excuses! YOU can do ANYTHING you put your mind to! Get to it cause you can do it🤗 Thank You again for being here with me.. sending love & hugs.. LL & squad 
Here's the link: www.forbes.com/top-influencers/fitness
